<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #EEFFFF">console</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">log</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(arr</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">join</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&#39;</span><span style="color: #C3E88D">-</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&#39;</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">))</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">// 小艺-芹菜-小宇</span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br><span class="line-number">7</span><br><span class="line-number">8</span><br><span class="line-number">9</span><br><span class="line-number">10</span><br></div></div><h3 id="reverse" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#reverse" aria-hidden="true">#</a> reverse()</h3>
<p>将数组中元素位置颠倒,并改变数组内容</p>
<p><code v-pre>DEMO</code> reverse</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="shiki" style="background-color: #212121"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #C792EA">var</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> arr </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">=</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> [</span><span style="color: #F78C6C">5</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">2</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">6</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">7</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">1</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">]</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">// [5, 2, 6, 7, 1] =&gt; [1, 7, 6, 2, 5] 颠倒反转,没有排序功能</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #EEFFFF">console</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">log</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(arr</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">reverse</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">())</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">// 可做加密方法 借助reverse</span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br></div></div><h3 id="sort" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#sort" aria-hidden="true">#</a> sort()</h3>
<p>给数组排序(从大到小或从小从大)</p>
<ul>
<li>括号内可以使用<code v-pre>比较函数</code>,此函数有2个参数,用来决定排位顺序</li>
<li>固定写法
<ul>
<li>function (a, b) {
从小到大
return a - b;
从大到小
return b - a;
}</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th style="text-align:center">a-b的值</th>
<th style="text-align:center">排序</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center">小于0</td>
<td style="text-align:center">a会排在b之前</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center">等于0</td>
<td style="text-align:center">位置不变</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center">大于0</td>
<td style="text-align:center">b会排在a之前</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><code v-pre>DEMO</code> sort</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="shiki" style="background-color: #212121"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #C792EA">var</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> arr </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">=</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> [</span><span style="color: #F78C6C">5</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">2</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">6</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">7</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">1</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">]</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #EEFFFF">console</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">log</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(arr</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">sort</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">())</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">// 1 2 3 4 5 从小到大</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #EEFFFF">console</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">log</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(arr</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">sort</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">()</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">reverse</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">())</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">// 5 4 3 2 1 从大到小,此方法不适用</span></span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br></div></div><p><code v-pre>DEMO</code> 双位数排序</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="shiki" style="background-color: #212121"><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #C792EA">var</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> arr </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">=</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> [</span><span style="color: #F78C6C">5</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">12</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">36</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">27</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #F78C6C">1</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">]</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">// 从小到大[1, 5, 12, 27, 36] </span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">// 如果直接使用sort会出现双位数排序问题,</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">// 需要比较函数来解决</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #EEFFFF">console</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">log</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(arr</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">sort</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #EEFFFF">    </span><span style="color: #C792EA">function</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">(</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">a</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> b</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">)</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">{</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #F07178">        </span><span style="color: #89DDFF; font-style: italic">return</span><span style="color: #F07178"> </span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">a</span><span style="color: #F07178"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">-</span><span style="color: #F07178"> </span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">b</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #F07178">    </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">}</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #EEFFFF">))</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">;</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #545454; font-style: italic">// 从大到小</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #EEFFFF">console</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">log</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(arr</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">.</span><span style="color: #82AAFF">sort</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">(</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #EEFFFF">    </span><span style="color: #C792EA">function</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">(</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF">a</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">,</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> b</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">)</span><span style="color: #EEFFFF"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">{</span></span>
